                    </h4>
                </div>
                <div id="question5" class="panel-collapse collapse" style="height: 0px;">
                    <div class="panel-body">
                        <p>
                            Pay-per-click advertising is a simple form of marketing you can use to get your new business noticed and ranked on Google. It allows you to test various keywords, as well as headlines, selling approaches and prices. Pay-per-click will enable you to discover your highest converting keywords, so that you can use these more often on your website pages which would help your rankings on the search engine. This would eventually result in more traffic, more leads, higher sales and conversions. </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
